Package main.java.board

Contains the default classes and interfaces used in any type of board

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IChessboard
    Interface to manage the logical behaviors of any type of chessboard.
    IChessboardDisplay
    Interface to manage the displaying behaviors of any type of chessboard.
    IMove
    Interface to manage the movement behaviors of a piece in any type of chessboard.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChessboardDisplay
    Abstract Class to manage the displaying of any type of chessboard.
    ChessboardLayout
    Class to manage the layout of a given Chessboard.
    Square
    Class to represent a chessboard square
